1. *Otvoren* je vrata i svi su ušli u restoran. (The door was opened and everyone entered the restaurant.)
2. On je *otvorio* knjigu i počeo da je čita. (He opened the book and started reading it.)
3. *Otvorena* je nova radnja u našem gradu. (A new store has been opened in our town.)
4. Oni imaju *otvorenu* vezu. (They have an open relationship.)
5. *Otvoreno* se reklo da je on kriv. (It was openly said that he was guilty.)